	Fixed slapd ACL sets URI attrs (ITS#5384)
	Fixed slapd invalid entryUUID filter (ITS#5386)
	Fixed slapd-bdb idlcache on adds (ITS#5086)
	Fixed slapd-bdb crash with modrdn (ITS#5358)
